     network services simultaneously.  Tym/COMM 4.0 also contains TYMGEN ,
     a menu-driven program that makes it easy to set operating parameters,
     even for novice users.

     Other enhancements include approximately 20 new procedure statements,
     variable support, and expanded appendices in the user's manual.

